OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thu 7 May to Sat 16 May
OL,6,FThere is a lot of uncertainty in the
OL,7,Fevolution through this period, more so
OL,8,Fthan normal, but overall it would
OL,9,Fappear that a changeable theme is most
OL,10,Flikely. Most places are therefore
OL,11,Flikely to see some rain or showers at
OL,12,Ftimes, but also some drier, brighter
OL,13,Fweather. The emphasis on wetter
OL,14,Fconditions may be more towards the
OL,15,Fsouth and east at first, with low
OL,16,Fpressure perhaps more likely towards
OL,17,Fthe south or east of the UK, before
OL,18,Fshifting further north later in the
OL,19,Fperiod as low pressure becomes more
OL,20,Flikely to set up to the north or
OL,21,Fnortheast of the UK. After a cold
OL,22,Fstart to the period, especially in the
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Fnorth, temperatures are likely to
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
OL,24,Freturn to around average later.
FL,164,160,301,260,100,100
PN,16303
SC,0003
CT,20,T
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1777734667
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G3/3
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 17 May to Sun 31 May
OL,6,FLow pressure systems are likely to
OL,7,Fdominate across the UK at the start of
OL,8,Fthis period. This means showers or
OL,9,Flonger spells of rain are likely at
OL,10,Ftimes, heavy in places, with the
OL,11,Fwettest conditions probably towards
OL,12,Fthe northwest. There will, however,
OL,13,Fprobably be some dry and warm
OL,14,Finterludes, these more likely towards
OL,15,Fthe south, although temperatures are
OL,16,Flikely to be close to normal overall.
OL,17,FLater in the month, more settled and
OL,18,Fdrier conditions may begin to develop,
OL,19,Fwith temperatures perhaps rising above
OL,20,Fnormal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,164,160,301,260,100,100
